title: scan = a series of `run`s, first of length 1
pid: 420068e3-f8a8-4d10-9e1b-9cc7b22b0056
body: |2-
  These should sound different, shouldn't they?
  #+BEGIN_SRC haskell
    d1 $ (s "bleep" |*| speed (run 4))
      <> s "hc*4"

    d1 $ (s "bleep" |*| speed (scan 4))
      <> s "hc*4"
  #+END_SRC
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
